			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Your lilting words take to the wind, calming the wrath of nature for a short while.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Alternative Reward</b><b>:</b> Fey Magic Gift - Uncommon</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power âœ¦ Daily (Standard Action)</b></p><p><i>Effect:</i> You create a zone in a close burst 20 that lasts for 6 hours. The severity of weather in the zone is drastically reduced. A blizzard becomes a gentle snowfall, torrential rain becomes a light mist, and a howling gale is reduced to a gentle breeze. Creatures in the zone gain a +5 power bonus to Endurance checks caused by weather, and weather cannot heavily obscure the zone; it can only lightly obscure it.</p>",
